/// @func bbmod_shader_register(_name, _shader)
///
/// @desc Registers a shader.
///
/// @param {String} _name The name of the shader.
/// @param {Struct.BBMOD_Shader} _shader The shader.
function bbmod_shader_register(_name, _shader)
{
